<HEADLINE> 3 Children Dead in Apartment Fire  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEWPORT NEWS, Va. (AP) -- Three children died in an apartment
fire Wednesday night, authorities said.
</P>
<P>
   Firefighters were called to the scene of the townhouse
apartments about 10:30 p.m., police spokeswoman Dierdre Raines
said. She said one child was pronounced dead at the scene and the
others died at local hospitals.
</P>
<P>
   ''At this point, I don't have a lot of detail,'' Raines said.
</P>
<P>
   The cause of the blaze wasn't immediately known.
</P>
